This happened today: 'The key now is to get the Strait of Hormuz, try to restore production in the Gulf, and get oil production back up to where it was.

00:25:35.210 --> 00:25:49.560
It's going to be months, if not a year or two, before they can restore production to where it was on February 28th.

00:25:53.920 --> 00:26:00.453
The economic tsunami—I'll call it that—this wave that's going to sweep the world is going to create economic damage on par with what we saw during...

00:26:00.453 --> 00:26:15.680
well, we didn't see it, neither you nor I were born, but during the Great Depression of the 1930s.

00:26:24.380 --> 00:26:24.645
I just got a taste of it yesterday visiting with one of my neighbors who has a ranch.

00:26:26.400 --> 00:26:26.720
I'm in Manatee County, Florida.

00:26:39.863 --> 00:26:40.251
You know, 25 years ago, Manatee used to have 120 cattle ranches.

00:26:40.251 --> 00:26:45.524
Now they're down to like 10 or 11.

00:26:45.524 --> 00:26:53.560
So the rest of the cattle ranches have sold out, and they're building homes.

00:26:53.560 --> 00:27:01.440
Anyway, I asked him, "How's it going with your cattle ranch?

00:27:01.440 --> 00:27:14.776
"' He goes, "Well, number one, we're paying $2 more a gallon for diesel, so our fuel costs are way up.

00:27:14.776 --> 00:27:17.969
Our fertilizer cost has tripled.

00:27:20.680 --> 00:27:24.102
" And then he said, "I've got a problem because we've had a drought.

00:27:24.102 --> 00:27:29.990
This was not a consequence of attacking Iran, but we've had a drought.

00:27:37.360 --> 00:27:42.160
" And as a consequence of that drought, he has to supplement the cattle feed with hay that they'll eat.

00:27:49.350 --> 00:27:50.750
He said last year he would buy 40 bundles at $40 a bundle, so $1,600.

00:27:52.331 --> 00:28:02.630
This year, you can't find—he needs 90 bales of hay and that's selling at more like $100 a bale.

00:28:02.630 --> 00:28:16.011
So all of a sudden he's gone from $1,600 to almost $9,000 just to keep the cattle fed, to keep them alive.

00:28:19.965 --> 00:28:24.200
Now that's happening not just to him; that's happening across the United States to farmers everywhere.

00:28:24.200 --> 00:28:29.058
Particularly, the diesel fuel costs are up, and it's happening to farmers overseas.

00:28:29.058 --> 00:28:34.185
So the potential for a significant food crisis as some of these farms collapse or go bankrupt.

00:28:34.185 --> 00:28:38.276
They can't continue in business.

00:28:38.276 --> 00:28:40.640
They're not able to harvest the crops.

00:28:40.640 --> 00:28:43.044
So that's what I'm saying.

00:28:53.224 --> 00:28:53.628
The political-economic effects of this war have yet to even be felt.

00:28:53.628 --> 00:29:00.418
Then we're seeing the commodity markets, particularly the oil markets; they're not normal.

00:29:00.418 --> 00:29:20.000
I mean, there are some shenanigans going on because when the tanker arrives at port, the oil that's coming off that tanker is going for about $140 to $150 a barrel.

00:29:20.000 --> 00:29:25.032
In fact, I saw in Singapore it's $210 a barrel.

00:29:25.032 --> 00:29:25.880
That's pretty amazing.

00:29:42.111 --> 00:29:51.600
I didn't know anything about Singapore and the $210 because the Lord showed me $200 a barrel and I was praying over that.

00:30:00.760 --> 00:30:01.080
I hadn't seen that, son.

00:30:01.080 --> 00:30:02.040
That's amazing.

00:30:02.040 --> 00:30:07.320
So 150, that's a lot.

00:30:10.680 --> 00:30:26.800
And so we see the results of things that we knew were coming because the Lord and I saw great anti-Semitism coming towards the Jewish people and it came out of what's going on with Iran right now.

00:30:41.240 --> 00:30:54.840
And so the part that I was concerned about was Braden talking about the cattle because I saw genetically grown, lab-grown meat trying to be really pushed in the days ahead when a new type of virus comes out for cattle.

00:30:54.840 --> 00:31:06.022
And I saw them saying, "We're going to try to push worm burgers and cricket burgers.

00:31:06.022 --> 00:31:10.010
" Do you remember me giving the word about that?

00:31:10.010 --> 00:31:26.187
Cricket burgers, worm burgers, bug burgers, saying, "Hey, we have to have an alternative meat source because meat is too expensive.

00:31:26.187 --> 00:31:32.000
There's something wrong with the cattle, and there is the drought and all this.

00:31:35.920 --> 00:31:37.747
" And I said, "What, these farmers are going to be dumping the cows?

00:31:53.108 --> 00:31:53.320
" And I saw organic meat farming was skyrocketing; people were making big bucks off organic meat because they say, "Listen, this is organic.

00:31:53.320 --> 00:31:59.744
This is right off the farm, without all the preservatives and all that stuff.

00:32:02.514 --> 00:32:03.440
" And so people were trying to find meat.

00:32:03.440 --> 00:32:10.500
So it goes with the end times where we are.

00:32:14.840 --> 00:32:23.455
I truly believe these are the signs and the times of the birthing pains as we see the days approaching.

00:32:34.100 --> 00:32:34.595
The birthing pains are becoming more and more.

00:32:34.595 --> 00:32:44.230
It's like some family members that say they're going to raise quail and rabbits and other things like chickens; people are talking like that.

00:32:44.230 --> 00:32:55.090
It's all trying to think how to get ahead of the curve of what we believe are the birthing pains and the beginning of the sorrows.

00:32:55.090 --> 00:33:05.440
So that the body of Christ is the head and not the tail, above and not beneath.

00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:29.240
Now, I'm not telling you to store up your 30-year food supply and have a garage full of it, but it's interesting where the Holy Spirit is leading some people because of where they live and where they're able to do it.

00:33:29.240 --> 00:33:42.632
Now, somebody in New York City is going to be a lot different than somebody that's in the country in Oklahoma.

00:33:42.632 --> 00:33:50.796
God has a plan for every single one of us.

00:33:56.600 --> 00:34:01.816
And whatever he tells you to do, do it.

00:34:01.816 --> 00:34:21.259
So, I can't sit here and tell you, "Well, you live in LA and you live in New York City and then you live in Leach, Texas," and it's totally different because it's a different economy everywhere.

00:34:21.259 --> 00:34:35.285
It's like somebody said, "Do you know it's $25 an hour for parking in LA to go downtown?

00:34:35.285 --> 00:34:37.493
" $25 an hour to park your car!

00:34:37.493 --> 00:34:41.569
Just to park your car, to get out of the car.

00:34:41.569 --> 00:34:46.124
25 bucks an hour and they were saying it's over $9 a gallon for gas.

00:34:49.919 --> 00:34:50.632
I can't even imagine that kind of stuff.

00:34:50.632 --> 00:34:52.479
I'm just going, "What is going on?

00:34:53.080 --> 00:35:00.840
" But that shows $9 a gallon average in LA, and I'm thinking that's a lot of money for a gallon of gas.

00:35:00.840 --> 00:35:08.251
But I saw a mass exodus of major cities: LA again, Chicago, Boston, New York.

00:35:08.251 --> 00:35:18.680
People fleeing over this summer to the point they were all coming to Central Park and the South trying to like—we've had enough.

00:35:18.680 --> 00:35:25.883
People in New York are saying, "We've had enough.

00:35:44.010 --> 00:35:44.215
We can't live here.

00:35:45.465 --> 00:35:45.690
It's too expensive.

00:35:45.690 --> 00:35:50.664
We've got to pack up and we've got to move south.

00:35:50.664 --> 00:35:59.631
We've got to go to Oklahoma and these other cities that are down there and we'll populate those.

00:36:08.207 --> 00:36:12.460
" And I saw real estate in Oklahoma that would be hard to come by, rental homes and things like that in the days ahead because people were going to be leaving trying to flee this $25 for parking.

00:36:15.874 --> 00:36:16.263
"We can't afford to live here anymore.

00:36:16.263 --> 00:36:20.140
We can't afford this gas.

00:36:20.140 --> 00:36:23.200
" That's what people were acting like.

00:36:23.200 --> 00:36:39.349
And I remember in these visions I saw it, but it was by design.

00:36:39.349 --> 00:36:50.040
When they came, I saw tent cities, so much so that there were tent cities like Skid Row and people were all over the place, but revival broke out.

00:36:50.040 --> 00:37:01.920
I've talked about this for several years telling Brad, "I see fields full of people coming here trying to get a better life, but then they don't have enough to get here.

00:37:01.920 --> 00:37:13.908
" They are broke, and the finances and all the things that I have told about the finances—praying now, I've already talked too long; 28 minutes.

00:37:13.908 --> 00:37:20.114
But I just think it's interesting as we see these things happening on the news.

00:37:20.114 --> 00:37:24.102
Talk show people are talking about what's going on.

00:37:29.440 --> 00:37:29.947
And then one sister told us, "You have no idea.

00:37:29.947 --> 00:37:36.790
I live in Europe and you're not hearing what's truly happening in our country through your media.

00:37:47.640 --> 00:37:47.851
You're being censored to the point where you are truly not hearing what's going on in other parts of the world.

00:37:54.380 --> 00:37:55.680
" What do we not see through CNN, Fox, ABC, NBC, and wire news channels that we don't see on X or whatever?

00:37:55.680 --> 00:37:58.936
I'm thinking, "Is that true?

00:38:00.808 --> 00:38:05.760
" So, if that is true and you are in these other countries and you say, "Brandon, you all are clueless.

00:38:05.760 --> 00:38:09.560
What's going on over here?

00:38:09.560 --> 00:38:10.880
We live in Africa.

00:38:10.880 --> 00:38:11.910
Tell us.

00:38:11.910 --> 00:38:15.484
" Tell us in the comments down below.

00:38:15.484 --> 00:38:16.663
Say, "Y'all aren't here.

00:38:24.180 --> 00:38:24.385
You really don't know truly what's going on in Asia.

00:38:25.000 --> 00:38:29.564
You truly don't know what's going on in Africa or South America.

00:38:29.564 --> 00:38:35.465
You all are clueless what's going on in Venezuela right now because your media is not telling you.

00:38:49.160 --> 00:38:49.740
" And if that's true, tell us because I'm curious.

00:38:49.740 --> 00:38:53.650
We get these emails and I'm thinking, "Are these people just pulling our chain?

00:38:53.650 --> 00:38:58.410
" We get a lot of emails from all around the world all the time.

00:38:58.410 --> 00:39:06.173
Diana is continually telling me, "Did you know this is going on in this country and all this?

00:39:07.960 --> 00:39:08.383
" And I'm going, "Wow.

00:39:21.240 --> 00:39:21.547
" I realize I have so many people following me from all around the world.

00:39:21.547 --> 00:39:24.520
So, we're just old country people in Oklahoma.

00:39:24.520 --> 00:39:25.650
We don't know.

00:39:39.271 --> 00:39:39.775
But it's interesting because there's so many of you from all over the place.

00:39:39.775 --> 00:39:41.286
Let's pray.

00:39:41.286 --> 00:39:44.840
I'll give you just five minutes here.

00:39:48.984 --> 00:39:49.288
I saw Cuba a lot last night.

00:39:49.896 --> 00:39:50.504
I saw sniffers.

00:39:52.028 --> 00:39:53.876
And when people say, "What is a sniffer?

00:39:55.075 --> 00:39:56.725
" It was airplanes sniffing for atomic bombs—nuclear.

00:40:04.336 --> 00:40:04.512
I saw these sniffers going throughout...

00:40:05.040 --> 00:40:12.120
I saw sniffers that were on poles in major cities in Boston and these other areas.

00:40:12.120 --> 00:40:19.728
I saw that they had a way of being able to detect backpacks and suitcases, using some kind of sensor.

00:40:30.383 --> 00:40:30.714
It was able to sniff them.

00:40:42.636 --> 00:40:43.354
And that's what I was talking about.

00:40:43.354 --> 00:40:48.560
I'm not trying to be weird saying, 'Well, you're sniffing things.

00:40:48.560 --> 00:40:50.874
' No, that's what the Lord called it.

00:40:50.874 --> 00:40:51.905
It was sniffing.

00:40:51.905 --> 00:40:54.893
Now, like I said, I saw it.

00:40:54.893 --> 00:41:06.130
It looked like a big plane with a big nose, and it was an actual flesh human nose on a plane sniffing the land and the areas.

00:41:06.130 --> 00:41:12.191
I knew that was a symbolization of something, and that's why I said I don't know.

00:41:13.116 --> 00:41:15.880
I tell him I've seen a plane sniffing things.

00:41:17.427 --> 00:41:21.075
I see a plane flying through the atmosphere trying to sniff things.

00:41:21.390 --> 00:41:24.997
I see poles and electronics sniffing things.

00:41:29.533 --> 00:41:29.836
And the Lord said, 'This is not real sniffing.

00:41:29.836 --> 00:41:32.467
This is a detecting early alert system.

00:41:32.467 --> 00:41:43.840
' I saw Fidel Castro during the old Cold War last night, and I saw that he was given a weapon of mass destruction that they have hidden for decades from Russia.

00:41:56.280 --> 00:41:56.600
It was the Cuban Missile Crisis; it looked like a briefcase.

00:41:59.787 --> 00:42:08.320
It looked like some kind of thing that they were trying to hide underground in a mountain in Cuba, trying to cover it with some kind of metal.

00:42:12.818 --> 00:42:12.973
I kept hearing, 'Don't go at this with pride.

00:42:18.760 --> 00:42:19.000
Don't go at this with pride, for they have something secret inside.

00:42:19.000 --> 00:42:19.960
Don't be prideful.

00:42:19.960 --> 00:42:23.667
Don't underestimate your enemy.

00:42:23.667 --> 00:42:35.206
' I saw lead, and the Lord was showing me there's something about lead they used to hide this thing so it would not be detected through metal and mud.

00:42:36.571 --> 00:42:37.086
I don't understand it all.

00:42:42.320 --> 00:42:42.567
I am just seeing this in part, hearing in part.

00:42:42.567 --> 00:42:54.480
But I saw these brass hands that looked like giant hands, massive fingers like Fantastic Four, the rock guy—the way his body was rock.

00:42:54.480 --> 00:42:56.434
These fingers looked like rock, but they were brass.

00:43:00.520 --> 00:43:00.760
And the brass went up like a bowl.

00:43:00.760 --> 00:43:02.053
'That's it, son.

00:43:02.053 --> 00:43:05.093
Just like those hands.

00:43:05.093 --> 00:43:06.133
Do you see those?

00:43:06.133 --> 00:43:07.154
Show those hands.

00:43:07.154 --> 00:43:10.697
' They were that big, that thick.

00:43:10.697 --> 00:43:20.693
These big rock-looking fingers were brass and they went up like a massive bowl, formed around like a cup.

00:43:20.693 --> 00:43:28.000
And in the middle of the palm of the hand, Marco Rubio was standing there in a suit.

00:43:37.900 --> 00:43:38.040
I saw these hands embracing him; they looked like brass, shiny, and it was concerning Cuba.

00:43:38.040 --> 00:43:42.560
As he was standing there, the Lord said, 'This is personal to him.

00:43:42.560 --> 00:43:45.760
' I saw it was personal.

00:43:45.996 --> 00:43:51.147
I saw relatives, people that meant something to him who were attached to Cuba.

00:43:52.444 --> 00:43:54.640
I saw him rise up and I saw a liberation coming to the Cuban people.

00:43:54.880 --> 00:44:02.220
I saw our military, certain units with crosses that were symbolic to this.

00:44:02.220 --> 00:44:07.100
Now, I'm not going all into this for a reason.

00:44:07.100 --> 00:44:12.627
There's a lot of you who will never make it to the end of this video.

00:44:12.627 --> 00:44:26.967
I'm not trying to be snide; I'm saying there was a reason why the Lord waited until many of you left.

00:44:26.967 --> 00:44:33.080
But I try to give you what I feel in my spirit, too.

00:44:33.080 --> 00:44:36.040
If you want to pray with it, pray.

00:44:36.040 --> 00:44:37.289
I saw these hands.

00:44:37.289 --> 00:44:49.600
I saw that the guy who was over it had chemical warfare weapons for viruses that, when people got them, they got these big sores on their bodies that looked like fire ant bites, round like a half dollar.

00:44:49.600 --> 00:44:55.224
Some were sores and boils all over the body, full of white infection with a black center.

00:44:55.224 --> 00:44:57.064
It was nasty.

00:45:02.664 --> 00:45:02.952
I don't know if this was smallpox.

00:45:06.360 --> 00:45:10.960
But I saw a canister that looked like a cylinder with a biohazard symbol on the side.

00:45:10.960 --> 00:45:14.180
As I was praying, I heard 'burros'.

00:45:14.180 --> 00:45:16.360
Burro—Braden said 'burro' means donkey.

00:45:16.360 --> 00:45:22.109
As we were praying in Spanish, the Lord showed us about mules in the night.

00:45:27.143 --> 00:45:31.497
I saw the American Coast Guard with radar on the tip of their boat, spinning around, able to detect if there was trouble in the water coming towards America.

00:45:33.600 --> 00:45:40.800
I saw the United States Coast Guard heavily patrolling Florida, and they were not able to penetrate the patrol like they were when Joe Biden was here.

00:45:40.800 --> 00:45:42.935
Thank God for President Trump.

00:45:46.131 --> 00:45:46.280
I saw these patrol boats really doing their jobs.

00:45:46.280 --> 00:45:50.568
They knew they couldn't get past our first defenses, so they were trying to devise a plan.

00:45:50.568 --> 00:45:58.550
But the Lord said they don't have weapons like Iran does.

00:46:05.520 --> 00:46:11.805
The rockets I saw didn't have the capability to strap a payload like Iran would; they didn't have the ability to strike America like Iran.

00:46:11.805 --> 00:46:14.120
Now, if I'm wrong, I'm wrong.

00:46:14.120 --> 00:46:17.136
But that's what I saw.

00:46:17.136 --> 00:46:19.067
Now, you say, 'Well, Brandon, they do.

00:46:19.067 --> 00:46:21.240
' I saw that they didn't.

00:46:21.240 --> 00:46:24.460
If they do, then I missed it.

00:46:24.460 --> 00:46:29.391
But I'm telling you what I saw in the vision.

00:46:37.560 --> 00:46:37.800
I saw our heroes—our men and women that protect our nation.

00:46:37.800 --> 00:46:38.760
God bless them.

00:46:38.760 --> 00:46:45.768
The Lord said, 'Pray for them.

00:46:45.768 --> 00:46:48.920
' That's all I will say.

00:46:59.131 --> 00:46:59.463
And I saw cyberattacks coming to Cuba in the darkness again.

00:46:59.463 --> 00:47:08.640
I saw a liberation and the Lord said, 'Do this by surprise and keep your mouth shut, leadership, for don't underestimate your enemy.

00:47:08.640 --> 00:47:19.848
' Announcing things and too much chatter is not healthy for the people going in, the ones risking their lives as you sit behind a desk pushing a button.

00:47:19.848 --> 00:47:21.084
Be still.

00:47:21.084 --> 00:47:21.413
Pray for them.

00:47:33.215 --> 00:47:33.370
I saw the chatter in the still of the night, like in Venezuela.

00:47:35.905 --> 00:47:36.130
The Lord said, 'Watch this.

00:47:36.130 --> 00:47:37.030
Pray for them.

00:47:37.030 --> 00:47:42.787
' But out of retaliation, that which was in the mountain was used upon the land.

00:47:42.787 --> 00:47:46.940
The guy in Cuba is nuts—the leader.

00:47:47.460 --> 00:47:56.060
I saw a mountain glow with a ripple of a wave that looked like an atom bomb.

00:47:56.060 --> 00:48:04.360
It went straight up and off the side of a mountain in retaliation to him losing his position.

00:48:08.420 --> 00:48:17.080
I thought, surely he wouldn't do that to his own people.

00:48:17.080 --> 00:48:23.760
But it was on the side of a mountain, looking like a mushroom cloud.

00:48:30.240 --> 00:48:30.445
I saw Fidel Castro's face and his beard.

00:48:42.453 --> 00:48:42.676
The Lord said he got this weapon back when he was in power and he's had it the whole time.

00:48:42.676 --> 00:48:49.154
It was a trade with Russia—I don't know what they traded, maybe oil.

00:48:49.154 --> 00:48:52.387
It was during the Cold War.

00:48:53.133 --> 00:48:53.382
I heard 'KGB'.

00:48:53.382 --> 00:49:02.905
So that's a little rundown for those who don't want to pray with us, so you can keep up and maybe help pray.

00:49:09.320 --> 00:49:10.760
I can present it to you, and if you don't want to pray, don't.

00:49:10.760 --> 00:49:13.580
But I pray you do.

00:49:13.580 --> 00:49:23.840
Pray for Cuba, pray for our president, pray for them to make great decisions.

00:49:35.533 --> 00:49:39.444
We must take no counsel from the ungodly as we pray for Cuba and Iran, that this ends quickly and they get all the plutonium.

00:49:39.444 --> 00:49:39.809
Uranium.

00:49:39.809 --> 00:49:39.991
Thank you.

00:49:39.991 --> 00:49:42.263
We're not in Back to the Future.

00:49:42.263 --> 00:49:44.980
It's what the Russians are after.

00:49:44.980 --> 00:49:48.000
All of it is coming to a head, folks.

00:49:52.338 --> 00:49:55.413
I truly believe we're about to see some amazing things with the church, but as we see these things, it's going to get darker in the world.

00:49:55.413 --> 00:50:03.470
We're getting closer and closer to the Lord's return, and I'm excited to be a part of it.

00:50:03.470 --> 00:50:04.410
Are you?

00:50:04.410 --> 00:50:06.300
So let's pray.

00:50:06.300 --> 00:50:09.320
Was that a good highlight?

00:50:09.320 --> 00:50:11.320
Did I get enough?

00:50:27.810 --> 00:50:27.995
I could go into real detail, but I'd spend an hour on it and I don't want to.

00:50:27.995 --> 00:50:29.360
How long was that?

00:50:29.360 --> 00:50:31.750
Not too bad, 41 minutes.

00:50:31.750 --> 00:50:36.930
Father, we just thank you for the body.

00:50:36.930 --> 00:50:38.851
Ow, my elbow just popped.

00:50:48.780 --> 00:50:49.120
Did you hear that?

00:50:49.120 --> 00:50:50.680
Wow, that was loud.

00:50:50.680 --> 00:50:51.495
Goodness gracious.

00:50:51.495 --> 00:50:53.560
Thank you, Lord, I'm healed.

00:50:53.560 --> 00:50:54.977
Thank you, Father.

00:50:54.977 --> 00:50:56.556
My knees, my body...

00:51:20.520 --> 00:51:21.480
Thank you, Lord.

00:51:21.480 --> 00:51:23.116
I'm getting this weight off.

00:51:23.116 --> 00:51:25.006
Obesity is terrible on your joints.

00:51:25.006 --> 00:51:39.827
I'm telling you, the more I get this weight off, I tell myself again that I am never going to get back to that because I'm moving around better the lighter I get.

00:51:39.827 --> 00:51:42.994
Obesity is hard on your joints.

00:51:42.994 --> 00:51:49.200
Your joints are screaming, 'Please get this weight off!

00:51:49.200 --> 00:51:56.520
' As you're walking down the street, they're asking, 'What are you doing to your knees?

00:51:56.520 --> 00:51:57.640
' It's incredible.

00:51:57.640 --> 00:52:11.680
Weight is heavy, and when you carry a lot of excess on your body, your joints and ankles scream at you when you exercise.

00:52:11.680 --> 00:52:15.800
They are trying to tell you to get that fat off your body.

00:52:27.731 --> 00:52:28.063
We've got to be physically fit for the coming of the Lord so that we are able to live long and finish strong.

00:52:28.063 --> 00:52:40.053
There are so many of you who have so much inside of you, but like me, letting weight keep us held back prevents us from being able to help those around us.

00:52:40.053 --> 00:52:41.120
We're breathing hard.

00:52:43.075 --> 00:52:44.541
We snore when we sleep.

00:52:44.541 --> 00:52:55.080
With sleep apnea, you stop breathing and your body's telling you, 'You're too fat around your neck.

00:52:55.080 --> 00:52:57.507
You've got to get this fat off.

00:52:57.507 --> 00:53:01.493
' You've got to take care of your bodies.

00:53:14.360 --> 00:53:14.500
That's what the Lord has been on me so strong about: 'I need you to take care of your flesh so that you're able to live long and finish strong for what I've called you to do.

00:53:14.500 --> 00:53:19.420
' After a while, you just yield.

00:53:20.150 --> 00:53:23.672
You can find other things to eat that are better.

00:53:23.672 --> 00:53:31.384
I find little things that I like better than chocolate now, but it takes retraining yourself.

00:53:48.379 --> 00:53:49.518
I'm trying.

00:53:49.518 --> 00:54:01.600
It's so important.

00:54:11.520 --> 00:54:19.030
I see so many people in the body of Christ who are so heavy, too.

00:54:19.030 --> 00:54:43.542
Here I am, I'm still heavy, but I'm getting there.

00:54:54.320 --> 00:55:01.560
I still see such a need to talk about health because we are eating wrong.

00:55:01.560 --> 00:55:06.000
Fast food...

00:55:42.240 --> 00:55:42.740
I try to measure my food every day now.

00:55:42.740 --> 00:56:02.270
Subconsciously, food has been a vice for me where I just ate whatever I wanted.

00:56:02.280 --> 00:56:28.000
But now I measure it and try to be precise in how much I'm eating.

00:56:28.000 --> 00:56:47.600
I take the time to use a scale and say, 'There's ten ounces, that's all.

00:56:47.600 --> 00:56:54.190
' Or, 'Here's seven ounces.

00:56:54.200 --> 00:56:59.940
' Measure it and look at what's going into your body.

00:56:59.940 --> 00:57:04.320
The Lord said, 'I want you to weigh your food.

00:57:04.320 --> 00:57:10.400
Not just measure it, weigh it.

00:57:10.400 --> 00:57:11.360
Take note.

00:57:11.360 --> 00:57:16.690
' I have an app, and every single time, I document what I put in my body.

00:57:16.690 --> 00:57:26.333
It's not fun, but I say, 'Well, I had ten ounces of chicken and ten ounces of this.

00:57:26.333 --> 00:57:31.782
' I measure it and it keeps track of your macros, all the protein, and everything.

00:57:32.693 --> 00:57:35.903
It shows how much protein you had versus carbs, and it helps me.

00:57:38.880 --> 00:57:47.680
I look at it and say, 'No wonder I was almost 300 pounds.

00:57:47.680 --> 00:58:01.940
' Looking back, you think you're not eating that much, but then you see what a cup of yogurt is.

00:58:01.940 --> 00:58:10.060
This good stuff that Dina gives me for probiotics is good for your stomach and helps your bowels move.

00:58:21.064 --> 00:58:21.336
You have to keep that regular; it keeps your body flowing.

00:58:24.444 --> 00:58:25.560
You don't want backup in your colon; you want to keep your bowels moving.

00:58:25.560 --> 00:58:33.182
There's so much to a healthy lifestyle to keep us going so that we are able to live long and finish strong.

00:58:33.182 --> 00:58:40.465
I've been ignorant to it until the Holy Spirit got on me and I started researching.

00:58:40.650 --> 00:58:41.205
I watch Dr.

00:58:41.205 --> 00:58:44.189
Berg and others and study them.

00:58:44.189 --> 00:58:45.345
It's interesting.

00:58:45.530 --> 00:58:50.253
I just try to help you all because it's something that I've dealt with.

00:58:55.497 --> 00:58:55.874
We don't drink alcohol.

00:58:55.874 --> 00:59:01.300
I know a lot of people who do, but we don't touch it.

00:59:01.300 --> 00:59:03.623
My vice is coffee.

00:59:03.623 --> 00:59:07.951
I love Kona coffee and Jamaican Blue Mountain coffee.

00:59:07.951 --> 00:59:10.200
I could drink it all the time.

00:59:10.200 --> 00:59:17.474
I used to drink eight cups a day or more, and Diana said, 'We're going down to just two.

00:59:17.474 --> 00:59:22.560
' I said, 'No, we're not,' but I'm doing it.

00:59:22.560 --> 00:59:26.662
I'm pulling back a little bit.

00:59:26.662 --> 00:59:27.596
It's okay.

00:59:42.860 --> 00:59:43.120
You don't have to have eight cups.

00:59:43.120 --> 00:59:45.253
Drink a little tea, drink more water.

00:59:46.177 --> 00:59:46.743
That's why I get these waters.

00:59:46.743 --> 00:59:50.160
Someone blessed me with these, and I'm so thankful.

00:59:50.587 --> 00:59:55.040
I have Fiji water and I drink it throughout the day now.

00:59:55.040 --> 01:00:04.520
Megan loves it, but it doesn't always have to be those things.

01:00:04.520 --> 01:00:09.387
Just try to find things that are treats for you.

01:00:09.387 --> 01:00:10.623
Good water is a treat.

01:00:10.623 --> 01:00:12.780
I'm just trying to help you.

01:00:12.780 --> 01:00:15.913
If we don't get this stuff under control, we're in trouble.

01:00:42.880 --> 01:00:43.600
I see so many people in the body of Christ with diabetes who go to Billy Burke's lines and say, 'Please, I'm dying of diabetes and my liver's quitting.

01:00:43.600 --> 01:00:52.182
' They have cirrhosis of the liver, not because of alcohol, but because they eat too much McDonald's.

01:00:58.456 --> 01:00:59.112
I'm like, 'You got cirrhosis of the liver from McDonald's?

01:00:59.112 --> 01:01:06.269
' I got fatty liver disease from McDonald's, not from drinking beer.

01:01:25.310 --> 01:01:25.545
My goodness.

01:01:25.545 --> 01:01:30.011
They look pregnant because their liver is quitting.

01:01:41.560 --> 01:01:41.867
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, you've got to get this.

01:01:41.867 --> 01:01:50.660
' When I went for my labs, the doctor called me and said, 'What you're doing is working.

01:01:50.660 --> 01:02:01.267
' He said, 'Your labs are better than anyone I've seen in my clinic in a long time.

01:02:01.267 --> 01:02:20.249
Everything is perfect, even your testosterone is getting better.

01:02:20.249 --> 01:02:30.650
' He said he hasn't seen labs as good as mine in a long time.

01:02:34.970 --> 01:02:35.280
All my markers are in the green.

01:02:35.280 --> 01:02:38.280
He said, 'Brandon, you're doing it.

01:02:42.655 --> 01:02:42.900
You're really healthy.

01:02:42.900 --> 01:02:50.623
' There was only one thing I needed to work on, but all my minerals and everything were perfect.

01:02:50.623 --> 01:02:55.368
I give all glory to God.

01:02:55.368 --> 01:02:56.996
I said, 'Lord, you're keeping me.

01:02:56.996 --> 01:03:01.620
' The anointing will keep you just like Moses; his eyes didn't grow weary.

01:03:01.620 --> 01:03:02.897
They didn't grow dim.

01:03:02.897 --> 01:03:04.394
They lived long and finished strong.

01:03:06.470 --> 01:03:08.545
And here he was 120 years and he just gave up the ghost.

01:03:08.545 --> 01:03:09.485
He went home.

01:03:09.485 --> 01:03:15.360
But I'm telling you, we don't have to go home feeling like trash.

01:03:17.920 --> 01:03:39.008
And I thought, why not talk about health—certain bread, certain things, eating right, doing real good grains that are good for your colon instead of eating all the trash and the processed they keep feeding us for all the prescriptions and all the stuff they keep putting us on and the pharmacy?

01:03:39.008 --> 01:03:40.760
It's a hamster wheel.

01:03:40.760 --> 01:03:42.520
It just keeps going.

01:03:42.520 --> 01:04:38.147
We get on a certain pill and you got to take that the rest of your life, and then that pill makes this symptom over here and that pill doctors this symptom, and the next thing you know, they come to a Billy Burke meeting with a bag of pills that looks this big and you go, 'I'm on 17 different medications and this medication affects this medication and this one over here affects this one and I've got to have all six; if I don't take all six, I die.

01:04:38.147 --> 01:04:41.733
' And you go, 'But I need healing.

01:04:41.733 --> 01:04:47.480
' And I'm looking at it going, 'This is bad.

01:04:48.740 --> 01:04:50.000
I got a bag of pills.

01:04:50.000 --> 01:04:52.720
Look at this.

01:05:15.540 --> 01:05:15.815
You look like a medicine cabinet.

01:05:15.815 --> 01:05:20.360
' And you're going, 'My goodness, a pharmacy loves you.

01:05:20.360 --> 01:05:23.813
' And I'm not making fun of it.

01:05:23.813 --> 01:05:38.191
I'm thinking there's a problem when this pill affects this pill and you got the symptoms of this, and I got, 'Well, I'm taking Ozempic and I'm injecting it in my stomach and I've lost all this weight, but now my face looks like this and I don't know what to do with it.

01:05:38.191 --> 01:05:47.360
' My face looks funny and I look like I'm not even really human, but I look skinny.

01:05:47.360 --> 01:05:52.360
And then they say, 'Well, it's causing blindness in people.

01:05:52.360 --> 01:06:01.834
' Now people are going, 'I don't know how to see, but I'm skinny.

01:06:01.834 --> 01:06:08.200
I can't see you, but I'm looking good in my face.

01:06:08.200 --> 01:06:11.555
' And I'm like, 'There's a problem.

01:06:11.555 --> 01:06:15.737
' It's just being real with you.

01:06:15.737 --> 01:06:26.160
Father, we just thank you for the body, and Jesus paid the price for it, living health.

01:06:31.280 --> 01:06:31.463
But I think there's a lot to organic.

01:06:31.463 --> 01:06:34.960
There's a lot to growing your own food.

01:06:47.415 --> 01:06:57.750
And what I see coming—knowing how to do a garden, knowing how to grow tomatoes, knowing how to catch fish in a pond instead of buying packaged fish or whatever.

01:06:57.760 --> 01:07:08.505
Learning how to live off the land more like our ancestors did, being more attentive with things and saying, 'Listen, there's just something about it.

01:07:08.505 --> 01:07:13.766
' Finding a way, Father, I just thank you for your body.

01:07:13.766 --> 01:07:18.495
I thank you, Father, for all that you've done for us.

01:07:18.495 --> 01:07:33.000
I thank you, Father, for every person here tonight that we find that place of health that we don't have all these pills injecting and all these things going on in our bodies.

01:07:33.000 --> 01:07:36.733
But Father, we're so grateful that you paid the price for us.

01:07:36.733 --> 01:07:44.160
And you said you'd give us wisdom if we ask for it.

01:07:58.520 --> 01:07:58.944
And so I'm asking you right now, Father, right now in the name of Jesus, give these people wisdom.

01:07:58.944 --> 01:08:05.700
Give them wisdom on what to do with their bodies so they don't keep living this way.

01:08:12.360 --> 01:08:12.606
We need them.

01:08:21.710 --> 01:08:22.260
We need them on the other side of the camera.

01:08:25.160 --> 01:08:27.103
We need them to stay and live long.

01:08:27.103 --> 01:08:31.714
We don't want them going home when they're 50.

01:08:32.165 --> 01:08:35.960
We don't need them going home when they're 45.

01:08:35.960 --> 01:08:39.960
'Well, what's wrong with you?

01:08:39.960 --> 01:08:41.880
' 'I don't know.

01:08:43.836 --> 01:08:44.164
I don't feel good.

01:08:44.164 --> 01:09:00.610
' Father, we need them, for the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:09:04.858 --> 01:09:05.187
And it's all hands on deck.

01:09:05.187 --> 01:09:13.640
We need every brother and sister around the world, whatever they got to be able to add their supply.

01:09:18.847 --> 01:09:20.133
And so, Father, I thank you, Lord, that we have become more conscious with our health.

01:09:20.133 --> 01:09:22.297
Help me in my health journey.

01:09:22.297 --> 01:09:31.680
Every single one of us needs a health journey to take better care of our temples to represent you better.

01:09:35.279 --> 01:09:36.823
And Father, it's something I pray for every day.

01:09:36.823 --> 01:09:40.337
Something we struggle with, Father, in the natural.

01:09:40.337 --> 01:09:49.560
But I know that whenever I am weak, you make me strong.

01:09:49.560 --> 01:09:58.977
Help me and help us to help other people around us and that we walk in healing and health and wellness.

01:10:05.540 --> 01:10:08.760
And Father, that their marriages are good, that their children are healthy, and their spiritual health is good.

01:10:08.760 --> 01:10:20.320
I thank you, Father, that we're going from glory to glory and that we're not dissatisfied with where we are.

01:10:20.320 --> 01:10:51.000
No, I want to be in the place of overflow in my health, in my marriage, with my children, with the finances, with whatever God has for me.

01:10:53.160 --> 01:10:54.947
I want to live an abundant life.

01:10:54.947 --> 01:11:04.766
Father, that when we leave and if we go by the graveside, you look at us and you say, 'Well done.

01:11:04.766 --> 01:11:06.069
You did good.

01:11:06.069 --> 01:11:21.520
' I want him to say, 'You left it all on the field when you were playing the game.

01:12:03.420 --> 01:12:03.970
You left it all on the field.

01:12:03.970 --> 01:12:07.880
You didn't hold nothing back, son.

01:12:07.880 --> 01:12:13.736
' You tried, Father.

01:12:13.736 --> 01:12:15.430
I tried.

01:12:15.430 --> 01:12:19.520
I didn't let anything hold me back.

01:12:19.520 --> 01:12:22.257
At least go down fighting.

01:12:22.257 --> 01:12:26.440
Don't just lay over and let the devil run you.

01:12:26.440 --> 01:12:30.303
I'm going to run you back.

01:12:30.303 --> 01:12:36.251
I'm going to—good measure, pressed down—I'm going to sow my seed.

01:12:54.965 --> 01:12:55.190
I'm going to come after you with the sword of the spirit and the shield of faith.

01:12:55.190 --> 01:13:05.680
I'm going to knock your teeth in and I'm going to go down fighting.

01:13:05.680 --> 01:13:12.800
I'm not going to sit there and lie down and go, 'Well, woe is me.

01:13:12.800 --> 01:13:17.940
' I'm going to fight the good fight of faith.

01:13:17.940 --> 01:13:45.910
A good fight is a fixed fight and a fight that you win.

01:13:45.920 --> 01:13:47.840
But there's sometimes people go home.

01:13:47.840 --> 01:13:50.686
I'm not being ignorant to that.

01:13:50.686 --> 01:13:58.526
I see people that live and they live by faith and they go home.

01:13:58.526 --> 01:14:06.013
But to be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

01:14:06.013 --> 01:14:15.911
You still got the victory, but at least you went down fighting, not rolling over for the devil to run you down.

01:14:49.160 --> 01:14:50.126
I take communion.

01:14:59.733 --> 01:15:00.120
I believe with all my heart and I know because Billy talks to me about people.

01:15:00.120 --> 01:15:16.280
They believe him for healing for cancer and they don't receive it on this side of the earth and they die.

01:15:16.280 --> 01:15:18.864
There's been a lot of people that do that.

01:15:18.864 --> 01:15:20.520
Did they get whipped?

01:15:20.520 --> 01:15:25.520
Did they lose?

01:15:25.520 --> 01:15:33.015
No.

01:15:33.015 --> 01:15:54.791
They still overcome on the other side by the blood of the lamb and by the word of our testimony.

01:16:24.040 --> 01:16:24.733
We still get the victory even in death on the other side.

01:16:24.733 --> 01:16:28.280
Finish your race strong.

01:16:28.280 --> 01:16:40.280
Father, we thank you, Lord, for the body.

01:16:40.280 --> 01:16:41.560
And we do.

01:16:41.560 --> 01:16:47.280
We take this right now in Jesus' name.

01:16:47.280 --> 01:16:49.200
Thank you, Lord.

01:16:49.200 --> 01:16:51.680
Amen and amen.

01:16:51.680 --> 01:16:59.020
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

01:16:59.020 --> 01:17:15.509
And we take the blood and we apply the blood over us and we plead the blood over our minds, our emotions, our sleep.

01:17:15.509 --> 01:17:21.149
As we sleep, we sleep uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:17:21.149 --> 01:17:28.400
We have good dreams, sound sleep, not tormented by fear, not tormented by worry, not tormented by the boogeyman or whatever.

01:17:28.400 --> 01:17:30.080
I'm covered by the blood.

01:17:39.537 --> 01:17:39.886
And I thank you, Lord, you could protect my wife, my kids.

01:17:39.886 --> 01:17:50.236
Father, I thank you that you said, 'I've never seen the righteous forsaken or the seed begging bread.

01:17:50.236 --> 01:17:54.208
' He'll always take care of you.

01:18:05.880 --> 01:18:06.732
And I thank you, Lord, that you provide for us.

01:18:08.435 --> 01:18:15.027
I thank you, Lord, for creative ideas to get wealth.

01:18:15.027 --> 01:18:22.533
Thank you, Lord, for the blood that covers us from the top of our head to the soles of our feet.

01:18:23.280 --> 01:18:25.767
And we're going from glory to glory.

01:18:25.767 --> 01:18:48.735
Forgive us of our sins, Lord, all the things we've messed up on.

01:18:48.735 --> 01:19:04.853
Even whenever we don't even realize we did it, we know that it's all under grace and by mercy, Father, we are able to do it anyway.

01:19:04.853 --> 01:19:08.856
You're so wonderful, Father, that you took care of all of us.

01:19:19.371 --> 01:19:19.634
And amen and amen to that.

01:19:19.634 --> 01:19:21.189
We take the blood.

01:19:21.189 --> 01:19:25.257
Don't worry about everything, worrying and fretting all the time.

01:19:32.620 --> 01:19:32.970
It's a habit I have to break.

01:19:37.046 --> 01:19:37.969
Say, 'No, I ain't worrying about it.

01:19:37.969 --> 01:19:44.771
Not taking a thought about that.

01:19:44.771 --> 01:19:47.903
I take the care out of my thinking.

01:19:47.903 --> 01:19:55.990
' I'm not going to take the care of this.

01:19:56.000 --> 01:19:58.280
Worry will kill you all the time.

01:20:04.423 --> 01:20:07.476
Just sitting there worrying and fretting about things.

01:20:07.476 --> 01:20:09.022
What are you going to do?

01:20:09.022 --> 01:20:20.920
I think that's some of the things that I've overcome with high functioning.

01:20:20.920 --> 01:20:25.427
You'll fixate on things in the past.

01:20:30.570 --> 01:20:30.785
And so I break that off of me.

01:20:36.160 --> 01:20:36.560
You have to renew your mind with the word.

01:20:36.560 --> 01:20:39.355
We all got stuff we're overcoming.

01:20:39.355 --> 01:20:41.000
I'm just real about it.

01:20:41.000 --> 01:20:42.400
Isn't it a sweet presence, Braden?

01:20:43.800 --> 01:20:45.305
I think it's interesting when I feel like that.

01:20:45.305 --> 01:20:53.142
Surely the presence of the Lord is in this place.

01:20:54.566 --> 01:20:56.131
I can feel the brush of angels' wings.

01:20:56.131 --> 01:20:59.040
I see glory on each face.

01:20:59.040 --> 01:21:05.040
Surely the presence of the Lord is in this place.

01:21:05.040 --> 01:21:10.907
Surely you still got that one lined up for me, hun.

01:21:10.907 --> 01:21:11.973
I like it.

01:21:11.973 --> 01:21:21.940
'Surely goodness and mercy shall follow me all the days of my life.

01:21:21.940 --> 01:21:28.313
' And I shall dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

01:21:28.313 --> 01:21:38.295
And I shall feast at the table spread for me.

01:21:38.295 --> 01:21:46.646
'Surely goodness and mercy shall follow me all the days of my life.

01:21:46.646 --> 01:21:49.380
' I believe it, Father.

01:21:49.380 --> 01:21:54.180
And I shall dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

01:21:54.180 --> 01:21:59.160
And I shall feast at the table spread for me.

01:21:59.160 --> 01:22:03.960
He prepares a table in the presence of all your enemies.

01:22:03.960 --> 01:22:06.280
He prepares that table.

01:22:06.280 --> 01:22:09.320
He has it set.

01:22:09.320 --> 01:22:28.500
He has a big old pot roast or maybe if you're a vegan, you have some cabbage or something.

01:22:28.500 --> 01:22:47.933
But either way, you're enjoying it and he has it all there and you're just enjoying your cabbage soup and I'm enjoying my pot roast because I eat meat.

01:22:47.933 --> 01:22:51.520
But we're all having a good time together.

01:22:51.520 --> 01:22:54.234
He has it spread there.

01:22:54.234 --> 01:22:58.005
He doesn't even care if you like meat or not.

01:22:58.005 --> 01:23:25.813
He says, 'I don't care if you're vegan.

01:23:25.813 --> 01:23:44.000
' And I got a lot of vegans watching me.

01:23:47.063 --> 01:23:49.500
I say, 'Hey, Brandon, I don't like it.

01:23:49.500 --> 01:23:50.640
You like eating meat.

01:23:50.640 --> 01:23:56.750
' That's okay.

01:23:56.760 --> 01:24:06.100
We can agree to disagree, but I'll watch you eat your cabbage.

01:24:06.100 --> 01:24:10.436
I'll eat it with you.

01:24:10.436 --> 01:24:13.650
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

01:24:13.650 --> 01:24:22.506
We're all so fearfully and wonderfully made.

01:24:22.506 --> 01:25:06.040
He loves each and every one of us, and he prepares that table before us in the presence of all our enemies and he's up there saying, 'I've got a plan for your life.

01:25:06.040 --> 01:25:09.560
' So, Father, right now, we pray over that plan for every single one of them.

01:25:09.560 --> 01:25:32.258
Father, there's so many of them there right now that are asking, 'What is your plan for my life?

01:25:32.258 --> 01:25:34.640
' And they don't know.

01:25:34.640 --> 01:25:37.776
